<span id="freeTextContainer17649608890269559697">Oh my God! What a read! In all my life I have never come across a book such as The Isolation Of X. I found that Lyra Jade explains something new and wonderful that I have never seen addressed by any other Author. I also never thought I would ever become so emotionally attached to the characters I read about but The Isolation Of X did just that. I found it extremely entertaining, dramatic, gripping and enlightening and it left me with a feeling too difficult to explain. There are no boring spots,</span>
  <span id="freeText17649608890269559697" style="display:none">Oh my God! What a read! In all my life I have never come across a book such as The Isolation Of X. I found that Lyra Jade explains something new and wonderful that I have never seen addressed by any other Author. I also never thought I would ever become so emotionally attached to the characters I read about but The Isolation Of X did just that. I found it extremely entertaining, dramatic, gripping and enlightening and it left me with a feeling too difficult to explain. There are no boring spots, a real roller coaster that’s why I wanted more although I was satisfied. I laughed, I cried and it gave me a new perspective that I found to be extremely helpful. I would love to see this get made into a movie. In my opinion it’s a masterpiece!</span>
